@startuml
title 05. LangGraph Orchestration (Target Flow)

skinparam shadowing false

[*] --> load_context
load_context --> select_tools
select_tools --> execute_tools
execute_tools --> finalize_context
finalize_context --> compose_response
compose_response --> [*]

note right of compose_response
- endpoint/A2A response contracts stay outside graph internals
- compose is final-answer only
- no MCP recall in compose
end note

@enduml
